# r2-rocker .gitignore
# Establish before any secrets land in the working tree.
# See specifications/SECRETS-POLICY.md for what counts as a secret and why.

# ──── Secrets ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Trust group private key — the signing authority's secret.
# Only the *public* TG cert is committed (trust_keys/tg_cert.bin or .pub).
trust_keys/*_priv*
trust_keys/*_secret*
trust_keys/*.priv
trust_keys/*.key
trust_keys/private/
trust_keys/secrets/

# Generic private-key file patterns (defence in depth — github secret-scanning
# triggers on these, even in private repos under some org policies).
*.pem
*.p12
*.pfx
*_priv.bin
*_secret.bin
id_rsa
id_ed25519
id_ecdsa
*.ppk

# WiFi credentials (compile-time fallback). Commit only the .example.
firmware/**/wifi_config.toml
!firmware/**/wifi_config.toml.example

# Per-device NVS dumps (contain Ed25519 device keys).
*.nvs
nvs_*.bin
device_*.bin

# Dashboard runtime state (contains device pks + per-device calibration
# matrices). Local-only by default; export selectively for the paper.
dashboard/.state/
dashboard/calibration.json
dashboard/peers.json

# ──── Build artefacts ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
target/
build/
**/Cargo.lock.bak
*.bin.bak

# ESP-IDF / esp-idf-svc generated
sdkconfig
sdkconfig.old
managed_components/
dependencies.lock

# ESP-IDF SDK + Python venv that `embuild` downloads on first build.
# Multi-gigabyte; reproduced by any developer running `cargo build`.
.embuild/
**/.embuild/

# Build-time-generated sdkconfig fragments (host-specific absolute paths).
**/sdkconfig.partitions.generated
**/sdkconfig.*.generated

# ──── External / vendor reference material ────────────────────────────
# Vendored snapshot directories under docs/ retain only their files,
# not their original .git history. PROVENANCE.md inside each documents
# the upstream URL.

# ──── Editor / OS cruft ───────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.claude/settings.local.json

# ──── Logs / scratch ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
scratch/
tmp/
